# Ignore C/C++ source files - we only need the compiled binaries
**/deps/
**/src/
**/*.c
**/*.cc
**/*.cpp
**/*.h
**/*.o
**/*.a

# Ignore build artifacts except the final .node files
**/build/
!**/build/Release/
**/build/Release/*
!**/build/Release/*.node

# Ignore unnecessary files
**/.npmignore
**/binding.gyp
**/Makefile
**/*.md
!README.md